default other parts. For th
defaulte
defaultse 
defaultlatter 
defaultspecies, the list should contain an indication of the Member States/regions where the species is non-native, and the Regulation should apply in those areas only. Member States where the species is native can legitimately decide to trade or otherwise use the species, but may need to adopt measures to prevent the species from being transported by human agency elsewhere. 
